{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji43","name":"毛泽东全集第43卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji43.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给张维的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给张维的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1960年9月2日）楚珩兄："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惠书收读，甚为高兴。下次赴沪时当图良唔。你应好好养病，不要忧虑。如有困难，率直告我，不要藏在脑中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝你愉快！并候张夫人好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六○年九月二日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]张维，字楚珩，早年和毛泽东有较多交往。当时任上海第二军医大学教授。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":9,"day":2}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":489,"page_end":489},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}